Requires glm (On Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install libglm-dev)
Requires libjsoncpp (On Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install libjsoncpp-dev)

Currently this doesn't do anything with an octree. It just visualizes four 
points that I made up, then reads the JSON file from ../data/chappes_sml.json.

WASD: move in X and Z direction
Q, E: Move in Y direction



